<h4>How to delete a car</h4>
<p>
    You have to be logged in and have the car created to delete it. To do so, you need to open your personal profile page by clicking on
    your name up on the right side. On this page you can see My cars option in which the list of cars registered by you is shown. On the right side of each car in
    the end of the line is the option for Deleting the car. After clicking on the button the page for deleting is open. Be careful to choose the right car you want to delete. To make sure
    you chose the right one, all the information are displayed on this Delete Page. If you find out you do not want to delete exactly this one car, you can easily click on the Back
    to list button in the end and choose the right car. If you are sure you want to delete exactly this one car, click on the red Delete button. After
    this action the list of your cars is displayed again, but the car is not shown anymore as well as all its possibilities for creating a ride are not available anymore.
</p>
<h4>How to edit a car</h4>
<p>
    You have to be logged in and have the car created to edit it. To do so, you need to open your personal profile page by clicking on
    your name up on the right side. On this page you can see My cars option in which the list of cars registered by you is shown. On the right side of each car in
    the end of the line is the option for Editing the car. After clicking on the button the page for editing is open. Be careful to choose the right car you want to edit. To make sure
    you chose the right one, all the information are displayed on this Edit Page. If you find out you do not want to edit exactly this one car, you can easily click on the Back
    to list button in the end and choose the right car. If you are sure you want to edit exactly this one car, write the new information where it is needed and click on the Save button in the end
    of the page. After this action the list of your cars is displayed again with all the new information.
</p>
